<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020</DATELINE><TITLE>Health protection guideline of hotels reconstructed as isolation places for close contacts during the novel coronavirus pneumonia(NCP)outbreak</TITLE><BODY>This guideline stipulates the health protection requirements for hotels reconstructed as isolation places for close contacts during the novel coronavirus pneumoniaoutbreak, including requirements for hotels, personal health protection, and management. It is applicable to hotels reconstructed as isolation places for close contacts, such as general hotels, conference center, sanitariums, etc.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>